main event: A UFO sighting of a bright object ball with a three-foot tail observed over Cedar Lake, Wisconsin on November 30, 1962.
interesting points: The object appeared to be about 200 ft. in the air,The sighting lasted for only 2.5 seconds,The object was bright green and emitted white contrails,The sighting occurred at dusk,There was no attempt to recover the object or contact additional observers.
sighted object: bright object ball with a three-foot tail
witness description: a student from New Richmond, Wisconsin
